name: Pet of the Week – Annie
description: This week's Pet of the Week is the perfect pup to explore San Diego with - meet Annie! Annie loves to swim and play in the water and has plenty of energy to play and go on adventures.

affiliation.name: County of San Diego Communications Office

articleContent: This week’s Pet of the Week is the perfect pup to explore San Diego with – meet Annie! Annie loves to swim and play in the water and has plenty of energy to play and go on adventures. If you’d like adopt Annie and take with you on your adventures, visit www.SDDAC.com.
